      "content": "That's a good start, but can you actually include some specifics in the guide? Specifically, I want you to make sure they know that while the new system is faster, it might not have the same level of nuanced understanding or personalized touch that you provide. We don't want them feeling like they're just talking to a basic bot, so maybe point out some of the more complex travel itineraries you usually handle that a faster, more automated system might struggle with.",
